<p>Elliot Jay Stocks is a designer, illustrator, speaker, and author based in Bristol, England. He's also the founder and editor of <i><a href="http://8faces.com/">8 Faces</a></i>, a bi-annual printed magazine dedicated to typographic design, and one half of <a href="http://viewportindustries.com/">Viewport Industries</a>, a company who will be releasing a whole load of amazing stuff in 2012.</p><p>Elliot writes on <a href="http://elliotjaystocks.com/">his website</a> and tweets as <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/elliotjaystocks">@elliotjaystocks</a>.</p>